Subject: [PATCH] scsi: ipr: Fix softlockup when rescanning devices in
 petitboot

References: jsc#SLE-13654
Patch-mainline: v5.6-rc6
Git-commit: 394b61711f3ce33f75bf70a3e22938464a13b3ee

